OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThe US has struck Iran to respond to a
OL,8,Fdrone attack a day earlier on a cargo
OL,9,Fship in the Strait of Hormuz, a
OL,10,Fprovocation that President Donald
OL,11,FTrump said violated the ceasefire.
OL,13,FUS Central Command said the military
OL,14,Ftargetted missile and drone locations
OL,15,Fand coastal radar sites in Iran.
OL,17,FThe strikes came shortly after Trump
OL,18,Ftold reporters, "You'll find out,"
OL,19,Fwhether the US would respond to the
OL,20,Fdrone attack.
OL,26,@zD@QOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
