OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FOne of four drones fired at the ship
OL,8,Fdamaged its upper deck during the
OL,9,Fattack on Thursday, but the ship was
OL,10,Fable to proceed, Trump said. The US
OL,11,Fshot down the other drones, he said.
OL,13,F"We knocked down three of them. One of
OL,14,Fthem, I guess - we didn't miss it.
OL,15,FNobody saw it coming," Trump said.
OL,17,FThe UK has said that the container
OL,18,Fship was hit with a projectile off the
OL,19,Fcoast of Oman.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
