CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThe development came during a fragile
OL,8,Ftime for the US and Iran as they work
OL,9,Fto negotiate a permanent end to the
OL,10,Fwar. Iran has increasingly challenged
OL,11,Fthe region and the US over its control
OL,12,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, even with the
OL,13,Fcurrent interim deal it reached with
OL,14,Fthe US last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThe attack on the cargo ship happened
OL,8,Fwhile a United Nations maritime agency
OL,9,Fwas beginning an operation to move
OL,10,Fstranded ships out of the strait this
OL,11,Fweek, using an alternative route,
OL,12,Fhugging the shores of Oman rather than
OL,13,Fsailing through the central part of
OL,14,Fthe strait.
OL,16,FThe International Maritime
OL,17,FOrganisation halted the evacuations
OL,18,Fafter the attack and said on Friday
OL,19,Fthey won't resume until there are
OL,20,Fguarantees that the other ships won't
OL,21,Fbe attacked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
