FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FAbout 115 ships were able to move out
OL,8,Fof the strait in recent days, leaving
OL,9,Fabout 500 still in the area, said
OL,10,FArsenio Dominguez, the agency's
OL,11,Fsecretary-general.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
