PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FThe opening of the alternative passage
OL,8,Fthrough the strait was expected to
OL,9,Frelieve pressure on the world economy
OL,10,Fand remove Iran's main source of
OL,11,Fleverage in ongoing peace talks with
OL,12,Fthe US.
OL,14,FThe US and Iran are still negotiating
OL,15,Fthe terms of the deal, including
OL,16,Fissues such as getting ships through
OL,17,Fthe key strait and addressing the
OL,18,Ffuture of Iran's stockpile of highly
OL,19,Fenriched uranium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
