FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FUnder the interim deal, the two sides
OL,8,Fhave 60 days to work out the details.
OL,10,FShipping analysts said the drone
OL,11,Fstrike cast a shadow over what had
OL,12,Fbeen a growing stream of trapped
OL,13,Fvessels finally leaving the Gulf and
OL,14,Fan increasing flow of tankers carrying
OL,15,Fcrude oil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
