CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782609481
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in response to attack
OL,4,Con ship that Trump says violated
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,F"A week of widening commercial
OL,8,Fconfidence in the Strait of Hormuz has
OL,9,Fhit its first significant test," said
OL,10,Fmarine data company Windward on X. It
OL,11,Fsaid that while the strait remains
OL,12,Foperationally open with 43 transits
OL,13,Frecorded after the incident, "the pace
OL,14,Fof normalisation has slowed."
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, before Thursday's drone
OL,17,Fstrike, 78 vessels transited the
OL,18,Fstrait, the highest since the war
OL,19,Fbegan, although below the prewar
OL,20,Faverages of 130 or more per day.
